</div>
<div>
<p>　　<date notBefore="1119" notAfter="1125">宣和</date>元年<pc>，</pc>拜<term>尚書</term>右丞<pc>；</pc>
<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
